      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/39/732",
      "text": [
        " اَلْمَكَانِ اَلَّذِي يُصَلَّى فِيهِ فَقَالَ «إِذَا جَفَّفَتْهُ اَلشَّمْسُ فَصَلِّ عَلَيْهِ فَهُوَ طَاهِرٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.732 – Zurarah asked Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about urine that is present on a rooftop or in a place where one prays.\nImam (as) said: \"If the sun dries it, then you may pray on it, for it is purified”."
        ]
      }
    },
